reviewText: Initially, I thought Psychomania would be a another re-tread of Easy Rider but, no, it was pretty cool. Bought it for the Classic that is Alice, Sweet, Alice though.

I had these movies a long time ago, and I think the price I paid was well worth it! I have always thought the older movies were better than the new junk that comes out now anyway. And the vhs tapes last a lot longer than the dvds. I am so glad I found this on the internet. thanks!
